    "causal_summary": "Packet 021 built the bounded relation-inference backfill (`backfillRelationInference`) with two deterministic collectors and explicitly deferred the similarity `supports` and `contradicts` signals as best-effort extensions. This packet ships those two as OPT-IN collectors that reuse the same safety envelope: `dryRun` default true, bounded by `limit`, every edge `created_by='auto'` so it inherits `insertEdge`'s runtime guards.",
